'''Mind control''', contrary to popular belief, is [[serious business|serious fucking business]]. Do you often [[batshit insane|hear voices]] but fail to locate their source? Do you find yourself in locations and situations with [[alcohol|no memory of how you got there]]? Do you find yourself the target of cruel mockery for your attempts to read/write English as if it were non-case-sensitive and/or a programming language? Do you [[WolfJLupus|fuck dogs]]? Some will call you crazy, but the truth is that [[you]] are a victim of mind control! The [[government]], since it is evil and unsatisfied with its influence over the media, has been [[trolling|harassing]] you with electromagnetic fields since before you were born, and this can be proven by the [[fact]] that it gets little publicity. [[Liberal|Some]] will tell you that magnetism has no effect on the [[frosted butts|human body]], but they are puny carbon-based liars who do not even understand that [[timecube|linear time is lie]]. The man on the right knows the [[truth]], but evil academics keep him down by forcing him to smoke [[crack]] and build a tent out of his motorcycle and literature every night.

However, [[some argue]] that "people with [[porn|dirty minds]] [[asking for it|deserve to be]] [[propaganda|brainwashed]]".

